flowRoot.flowPara: Welcome to the Fly Creek General Store! We are open for breakfast, lunch, and dinner 7 days a week. Our Deli offers subs, sandwiches, soups, salads, and much more. Come in or call for our daily specials. Our grocery section covers all the basics. We also have a great selection of specialty products including sauces, salsas, marinades, granola. Our beer section has the domestic stand bys and a full selection of craft beers from across the US. Come join us for a freshly brewed cup of Green Mountain coffee.
